prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style sloth wearing a tiny, ridiculously festive party hat, hanging upside down from a tree branch, looking extremely relaxed and blissfully sleepy. Below the sloth, a single, beautifully decorated cupcake with one lit candle sits on the ground, seemingly having waited for a very long time. The text "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script in the center. The entire scene is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the sloth and branch. The overall mood is humorous and lighthearted.
